<HL>
   Who's News:
   Eaton Corp.
   Names Butler
   Chief Executive
   ----
   By Dana Milbank
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/05/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7
</SO>
